description:
Japanese gang member. Keisuke falls in love with her at first sight, and after successful trial of his skills she accepts him.
Keisuke is the one who tattooed a lizard on her left breast.
While captured by GPX Natsuko is tortured, but manages to free herself and Keisuke (creating his scar on the back with hot metal bar). She is shot to death in the process and Keisuke is later framed as her killer.
name: Komiya Natsuko
